{"tid":2472603,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[勸世從良] 藝術男 > 工程男 / IT男","createTime":"2021-04-02T13:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:35:28.000Z","uid":391931,"like":21,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a4de597c8088aecb65b85c1e3c7df939fce6fc00","tid":2472603,"uid":391931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcNT74K9JNtn7RSsQnQshdPyZrEn3sNNcpy391hsXmrf9?filename=ogpHf8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogpHf8s.jpg&h=df79aad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人類發展歷史有兩條線<br />\n一條是科技線  一條是藝術線<br />\n科學可以讓我們了解這個世界<br />\n藝術可以讓我們更好地了解自己<br />\n<br />\n藝術是想象力的載體<br />\n藝術的力量 <br />\n在於憑借一些簡單的圖案 符號 音調<br />\n把分散的人串起來<br />\n讓人類有共同的精神追求<br />\n<br />\n今後科學<del>可能</del>會被人工智能取代<br />\n但藝術不會<br />\n因為科學是這個世界的偉大<br />\n而藝術是我們人類的偉大"},{"pid":"4364e3258f4c5e54d03aed0b01cb222bd57759a2","tid":2472603,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"梵高白金卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23372beacddb7491f443c7a659821d2be03cb47b","tid":2472603,"uid":370374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"部份同意<br />\n有好多人唔應該讀STEM, 但原因只係數底唔好，唔代表有其他才華"},{"pid":"172db835daf050b8913a4d0fa185d1b20e1a92ea","tid":2472603,"uid":70159,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">今後科學可能會被人工智能取代<br />\n但藝術不會</span><br />\n藝術先會比AI玩爛,<br />\nAI要學點為止係好唔難<br />\n但要AI脫離一開始set左嘅rule係唔可能<br />\nalpha go都唔可能進化到一次行2步棋一樣<br />\n但比AI學哂所有畫,輸入哂d畫人類認為係點樣<br />\ngenerate一張&quot;表達開心&quot;嘅畫根本唔難"},{"pid":"167e79b9e5d53e6b843e625ed81c96e83204a6ca","tid":2472603,"uid":350062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:02:53.000Z","msg":"Why not both lol"},{"pid":"7c41c7427188d6b7d564f9d2231789c17c52c7a1","tid":2472603,"uid":140125,"like":12,"disli